      },
      "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "\"Dante's Chiron is set apart from the violent centaurs he commands: as wise guide and healer he channels his hybrid nature upward into knowledge and guardianship rather than downward into bestial appetite, an ascensional transcendence of the teriomorphic baseline.”"
      }
