      },
      "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Hermaphrodite is describe as a young man deprived from his masculinity becuase of his union with the nymph Salmace, who was desperately in love with him. This union happens inside a water source which traps him into a body with feminine characteristic, causing the loss of his masculine traits, adhering to the nyctomorphic symbolism of the mutilation."
      }
    },
